title: Adventure in Iraq (1943 War) Stranded in the Sands - Their Mission: Escape or Die Trying!

sources.title: Adventure in Iraq (1943 War) Stranded in the Sands - Their Mission: Escape or Die Trying!
sources.description:
Stranded in the desert, George Torrence (John Loder), Tess Torrence (Ruth Ford), and Doug Everett (Warren Douglas) are captured by Sheik Ahmid Bel Nor (Paul Cavanagh), who uses them as leverage to demand the release of his brothers imprisoned as Nazi spies. To survive, they must outwit the Sheik and escape his dangerous stronghold.

Original title: Adventure in Iraq
Alternative title: Green Goddess

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/9VYzRuwJtkc


Directed by D. Ross Lederman
Writers: George Bilson, Robert E. Kent, William Archer 
Stars: John Loder, Ruth Ford, Warren Douglas, Paul Cavanagh, Peggy Carson
Genres: Adventure, War
